name: Joycelyn Terry Wayne
description: I’m looking for strong-willed, confident, purposeful, sociable man who is ready to open his heart. I want him to be ready for serious relationships because that’s what I’m looking for here.I would like to meet a devoted, honest and calm man, who likes to lead the active lifestyle, see the life in the bright colors, who is energetic and full of life, who has his goals and try to reach it, who never gives up and has a strong will and high moral values. It would be great if he would be a romantic man and would give me much attention and love, who will support me in any situation and who would have the same views and principles in life.
